Melchor Ruiz [COPE]: &ldquo;Dani Ceballos will leave on a dry loan condition: no option or obligation to purchase. He still has a future at Real Madrid and both him &amp; the club agreed that he must get a considerable number of games under his belt.&rdquo;

Zidane: &ldquo;Bale? He&rsquo;s not a problem, I'm not going to say that a player is a problem. He could happen, he's got a contract, we'll see. Nothing has changed with Bale since June.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Zidane on Pogba: &ldquo;I always respond the same, I'm going to look silly. The club knows what we want, there's time ahead, today we're focused on these (preseason) games, let's see what can happen.&rdquo;

Thiago Alcantara: &ldquo;Bale at Bayern? If a top player like him wants to come, he is welcome.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Bayern Munich coach Kovac was asked if Gareth Bale enters into his club&rsquo;s plan for the upcoming season. His response: &ldquo;No.&rdquo;
